SEARCH
Package at.leisner.server.plugin

Annotationsschnittstelle Plugin

@Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(TYPE) public @interface Plugin
If you want to register a Plugin by the Server your Plugin class need this annotation and must extend from JavaPlugin
